<h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Set up two-factor authentication</h1>

<p class="govuk-body">To use the Transition Readiness Dashboard, you will need to set up two-factor authentication using the <strong>Google Authenticator</strong> app.</p>

<p class="govuk-body">Google Authenticator is a free two-factor authentication app.</p>

<p class="govuk-body">Download it on your mobile device by searching "Google Authenticator" on the Play Store or App Store.</p>

<p class="govuk-body">You can either choose to download this app to your work or personal phone.</p>

